articles.author: Eliza Mackintosh, Nathan Hodge, Uliana Pavolva Dalal Mawad and Nada Bashir, CNN
articles.title: Macron meets with Putin, leading Europe's diplomatic efforts to defuse Ukraine crisis - CNN
articles.description: In the tense standoff between Russia and Ukraine, French President Emmanuel Macron has emerged as a central figure in Europe's diplomatic efforts to diffuse potential conflict.
